<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">历来最</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>长</span></strong></span><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">的“十一黄金周”</span></strong></span></p>
